 online customer reviews indicate the support provided by the manufacturer of this DIY security alarm system is stellar. A support rep will walk you through installation if you need assistance. Additionally, the company is known for sending replacement parts with no questions asked.<br/><br/>"]},"id":"86d22343-c3fb-4201-8519-70187e21c8c2","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_58896","url":"/fortress-s02-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"john-carlsen","url":"/author/john-carlsen","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"John Carlsen","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"jN6fuw55cS2xYQi25mfgkg","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-02-24T16:31:29Z","datePublished":"2014-02-24T16:31:29Z","name":"Fortress S02-C","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been replaced by another product. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been replaced by another product. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.","language":"en","dateModified":"2014-02-24T16:31:29Z","id":"Z5w23GyARD8u3TBU3qK7RR","meta":{"title":"Fortress S02-C Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"The Fortress S02-C offers reliability and impressive customer support. It is one of the DIY security system customer favorites. Find out more in the full review."},"products":[{"slug":"fortress-s02-c","url":"/product/fortress-s02-c","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T18:38:27Z","name":"Fortress S02-C","dateModified":"2019-04-16T18:38:27Z","id":"4njxAgrzLWZVKnRCDuzLJ8","dateImported":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","site":"toptenreviews"}],"dateImported":"2019-04-16T18:38:27Z",